{"tid":2449948,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"指京毀港民主「不應為敗壞制度背書」 泰晤士報促終院10英籍法官總辭","createTime":"2021-03-17T04:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T05:11:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"afb692b65ab5edb99ec973ec3a3590ff661cc878","tid":2449948,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/M6RPYOMP2FGRDL2G4W4PF3H2M4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FM6RPYOMP2FGRDL2G4W4PF3H2M4%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=8ff74bc6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FM6RPYOMP2FGRDL2G4W4PF3H2M4%2F&h=e60a4498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/M6RPYOMP2FGRDL2G4W4PF3H2M4/</a><br />\n<br />\n指京毀港民主「不應為敗壞制度背書」<br />\n泰晤士報促終院10英籍法官總辭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LGt8c7egLPqxQZrpKjuxmukRIu4=/2263x815/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6V4H7GCU4VGZ7KR7TK4QQRILWE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLGt8c7egLPqxQZrpKjuxmukRIu4%3D%2F2263x815%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6V4H7GCU4VGZ7KR7TK4QQRILWE.gif&h=a0f2a52c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機用戶請按此放大圖表<br />\n<br />\n【兩制蓋棺】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】北京出手閹割香港選舉後，英國《泰晤士報》昨日公開促請十位英籍法官集體退出香港終審法院以示抗議。雖然已有兩名法官接受延任非常任法官，《泰晤士報》仍要求他們共同進退。<br />\n<br />\n香港終審法院現共有14名海外非常任法官，英籍的包括英國最高法院院長韋彥德（Robert Reed），最高法院副院長賀知義（Patrick Stewart Hodge）、最高法院前院長何熙怡（Brenda Hale）、廖柏嘉（David Neuberger）和范理申（Nicholas Addison Phillips）、最高法院前法官岑耀信（Jonathan Sumption）和前大法官郝廉思（Lawrence Collins），以及苗禮治（Peter Millett）、華學佳（Robert Walker）和南非出世的賀輔明（Leonard Hubert Hoffmann）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已有兩人接受延任<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士報》上周報道，韋彥德正審視英籍法官在港角色，即將對去留作出決定，但昨指廖柏嘉、華學佳和澳洲的紀立信（Murray Gleeson），都已同意延任三年。<br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士報》社論指曾幾何時，英國認為在1997年香港主權移交後，英籍法官。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對於廖柏嘉和華學佳接納港府最近提出續期三年的合約，《泰晤士報》認為事件已不單是司法問題，也涉及外交層面，雖。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n社論的總結直白：「（英籍）法官們要在沒有爭議聲中延續豐厚的客席合約，已是不可能的事，隨着他們以為可在新體制內帶來。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大律師公會不贊成<br />\n<br />\n香港大律師公會主席夏博義（Paul Harris）不贊成海外法官請辭，擔心此舉會進一步損害終審法院。來自澳洲的前非常任法官施覺民（James Spigelman）因不滿實施國安法，去年9月辭任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6SYoMhph181_KuZE5qB4spJNDUs=/1971x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2HOHFCFLJBCZRNTE2QW7H6BB34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6SYoMhph181_KuZE5qB4spJNDUs%3D%2F1971x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2HOHFCFLJBCZRNTE2QW7H6BB34.jpg&h=55966a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《泰晤士報》發表社論，促請英籍法官退出香港終審法院以示抗議北京對港的打壓。互聯網"},{"pid":"f1a82b9211e5ce72d8e9c46215d462bc223c239c","tid":2449948,"uid":55010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:04:12.000Z","msg":"點名開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1841caca75ed459f822b431b6efebd24e6e886c","tid":2449948,"uid":28202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:07:01.000Z","msg":"你唔請辭唔緊要,你咪出嚟講吓嘢,但你又無,好似當無事發生咁"},{"pid":"b87ec9a4870de34048adae2ea02f32be33824e1a","tid":2449948,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"唔請辭就視國安法而無物"},{"pid":"f1a19743552cb72dfb51fa24d298de37e2249083","tid":2449948,"uid":39777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:11:19.000Z","msg":"香港法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}